Paper: hep-th/0203133

Date: 2002-03-14

Title: Green Function for Spin 1/2 particle in a Coulomb + Scalar Potential

Authors: Arvind Narayan Vaidya, Luiz Eduardo Silva Souza (Universidade Federal

do Rio de Janeiro)Comments: 10 pages,no figures

We calculate the Green function for the Dirac equation describing a spin 1/2particle in the presence of a potential which is a sum of the Coulomb potentialV_C=-A_1/r and a Lorentz scalar potential V_S=-A_2/r. The bound state spectrumis obtained.